N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 43.15 - Reporting

State Regulations

In addition to any monthly reports otherwise required of
milk dealers and cooperatives pursuant to article 21 of the law, each milk
dealer and cooperative subject to the provisions of section 258-b of the law
shall as required by the commissioner file such other reports and information
as may be necessary for administration and enforcement of that
section. Notes
